WEBVTT

00:00:00.475 --> 00:00:07.405
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:00:14.394 --> 00:00:29.844
There is no such area/courtyard in
life where man does not search.

00:00:31.561 --> 00:00:39.721
Sometimes he doesn't know what
he is searching for.

00:00:41.646 --> 00:00:54.236
He doesn't know that there is something
lost within him that he is searching for.

00:00:55.234 --> 00:01:03.044
Superficially no matter how much he may
say, 'I am fine,' or 'I am satisfied.'

00:01:05.343 --> 00:01:23.263
But if he thinks from within, then
there is some quest hidden within him
which is calling him from every side.

00:01:28.020 --> 00:01:43.190
Sometimes he thinks that if I earn
a lot of money then I will surely
find contentment/solution

00:01:44.629 --> 00:01:54.369
And in his search of how to make
money, he does wrong things.

00:01:55.849 --> 00:02:04.269
But I have never seen any rich
person very happy, not till today.

00:02:05.450 --> 00:02:12.460
All those who come to Me say,
"Mother, in every way there
is discord in the house."

00:02:12.501 --> 00:02:17.551
"And I don't have any peace within
me, please give me peace."

00:02:18.117 --> 00:02:30.017
Then someone thinks that, "My physical
strength should increase so much
that the world trembles before me."

00:02:31.583 --> 00:02:36.573
And he keeps trying that,
"I should make my body strong."

00:02:38.747 --> 00:02:46.387
"Even then I don't get peace."
He also says, "Mother, give me peace."

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:54.570
After that many people run
towards power, work very hard

00:02:54.570 --> 00:02:57.323
'I want this power, I want that power.'

00:02:57.606 --> 00:03:03.546
I have seen even people with great
power that they have no peace.

00:03:05.173 --> 00:03:09.693
They also wonder where can this
peace be found.

00:03:16.145 --> 00:03:30.345
In this way man is wandering here
and there, running about in
search of peace.

00:03:32.429 --> 00:03:46.709
But where is this peace? Which
is that path through which this
peace could be found

00:03:46.709 --> 00:03:59.015
whereby we can know the secret of
this peace? If there is such an
auspicious temple, then people
roam around in temples,

00:03:59.015 --> 00:04:05.635
then go to some gurus and then
get lost in books.

00:04:05.963 --> 00:04:19.283
Whether they believe in God or not,
but all the time they feel that
there is no peace within.

00:04:22.754 --> 00:04:31.914
When man evolved from animal to
human, then he lost his peace.

00:04:32.761 --> 00:04:42.581
Because animals are in the control
(loop) of God, so there is no need
for them to be disturbed

00:04:44.367 --> 00:04:54.757
but there are two such institutions
inside a human being which do not
allow him to relax.

00:04:55.529 --> 00:05:03.959
One of those institutions, which
we can say, is ego.

00:05:05.832 --> 00:05:12.772
It is only man who thinks, 'I do
this, I do that, I did this,
I did that,'

00:05:12.772 --> 00:05:17.355
or 'I have to do this' or 'My
forefathers did this.'

00:05:20.553 --> 00:05:24.473
'What do I do next?' - he
thinks ahead.

00:05:25.094 --> 00:05:31.044
Which other special thing I want
to do - always thinking of the future.

00:05:31.890 --> 00:05:39.650
He is not at peace with what he
has at present. You know it is
said in Economics,

00:05:39.650 --> 00:05:48.457
in Economics, that the human wants
are never completely satisfied.

00:05:49.217 --> 00:05:57.027
You just see, today you bought this thing,
after that bought another thing -

00:05:57.755 --> 00:06:05.635
will go through so much trouble for
each thing and when they get that thing,
is achieved, it becomes worthless.

00:06:05.635 --> 00:06:13.011
Then started running after another
thing. When the other thing is got,
then after getting it,

00:06:13.011 --> 00:06:18.593
forgot everything how difficult
it was to get it, how much we
desired for it,

00:06:18.593 --> 00:06:24.607
forgot everything and thought
that it was useless, now do
something else .

00:06:24.887 --> 00:06:31.446
In this way a person's mind wanders
and starts running from one thing
to another.

00:06:31.509 --> 00:06:39.609
And he starts thinking, 'Look,
I have so many nice things.'

00:06:40.401 --> 00:06:49.621
Despite having everything, he does
not have peace within him. Still,
he remains restless.

00:06:52.029 --> 00:06:57.309
Some need one thing, some need
another. Some need things,

00:06:58.633 --> 00:07:06.393
some people desire for a home,
some people want children,

00:07:06.658 --> 00:07:19.248
then someone has a desire for power.
He runs after it and finds that
despite having all this,

00:07:19.389 --> 00:07:30.859
even though this whole ocean is in
front of me, just like a bird
remains thirsty in the ocean

00:07:30.949 --> 00:07:42.212
similarly, this ocean of the people
does not have the power to quench
my thirst.

00:07:48.052 --> 00:07:54.982
On the other hand, another institution
that has been formed within us, is
that of sanskaras (values).

00:07:55.609 --> 00:08:07.299
The values ​​start getting settled.
Someone says that from today onwards
do Surya Namaskar (prayer to the Sun)
every day.

00:08:09.547 --> 00:08:15.927
Now it's done that Surya Namaskar has
to be done. Now Surya Namaskar was
done today, was done tomorrow,

00:08:15.927 --> 00:08:21.654
was done the day after; done fifty
times, then a hundred times; in the
end got to know that he died of a
heart attack.

00:08:25.486 --> 00:08:31.366
If someone tells us some ritual,
then we go to the extremes.

00:08:31.923 --> 00:08:40.093
Despite having good values,
there is no peace in man/person.

00:08:40.738 --> 00:08:44.908
Like I know there is a gentleman,
he is a very honest man.

00:08:45.229 --> 00:08:50.589
He is so honest that he even points
out his wife's mistakes in front
of others.

00:08:54.206 --> 00:09:04.216
People call him honest, he is
such an honest man. But he does
not have peace in his mind.

00:09:04.927 --> 00:09:11.197
Why is there no peace within you
when you are on the path of honesty?

00:09:12.783 --> 00:09:17.173
And even then he will say, "See,
I could have earned this much money,'

00:09:17.173 --> 00:09:25.209
'But look, I'm honest, I didn't.
I didn't collect any money.'

00:09:25.222 --> 00:09:31.552
I don't think it is a special
thing for a person to be honest.

00:09:32.485 --> 00:09:39.625
Or there is a man who says,
'I speak the truth, I'm outspoken
too, I speak the truth.'

00:09:39.625 --> 00:09:48.512
'I speak the truth in every matter.'
But still he does not have peace
of mind.

00:09:48.658 --> 00:09:57.598
Only the values are present inside him.
So these sanskaras of religion which
are within us are from without.

00:09:57.598 --> 00:10:07.541
From that, it's just this that we
are pure people with pure conduct.

00:10:07.609 --> 00:10:20.289
But it's not empty yet, it's hollow.
No moistness of peace has come in it yet.

00:10:20.692 --> 00:10:29.592
There is no coolness of peace.
And most of the people who are
overly honest,

00:10:30.953 --> 00:10:37.263
they are so aggressive and short-tempered
- should always keep a distance of
five feet from them.

00:10:38.407 --> 00:10:46.557
Never know when they will push
you down because such people
have too much anger in them.

00:10:48.639 --> 00:10:56.259
Because this sanskar (value) is also
an imposed ornament, which becomes
cumbersome,

00:10:56.415 --> 00:10:59.875
whose burden cannot be borne by man.

00:11:02.030 --> 00:11:10.390
Similarly that, we have children,
we should take care of them,
we should insure them,

00:11:10.549 --> 00:11:14.739
there should be property for them,
this should be done for the wife.

00:11:14.739 --> 00:11:26.364
Thinking about many such things also,
man can not attain his peace.

00:11:26.576 --> 00:11:34.716
I was once very surprised that in
Maharashtra there was a very
sober(grave) man,

00:11:35.631 --> 00:11:50.041
and he made a very nice project by
making a very beautiful Varna Nagar.

00:11:50.041 --> 00:11:57.131
Thousands of people got jobs in
it and he made it absolutely such

00:11:57.131 --> 00:12:03.216
that it felt as if you have come to
a big city of some Western country.

00:12:03.216 --> 00:12:08.006
Well-organized provisions were made
for everyone, everything was done.

00:12:08.591 --> 00:12:17.171
So I thought I should meet this
great man and he expressed a great
desire that he wanted to meet Mother.

00:12:17.244 --> 00:12:23.594
When I reached there he grabbed
My feet and started crying.

00:12:23.594 --> 00:12:27.510
Such an aged man - I said,
"What's happening to you,
why are you crying?"

00:12:27.510 --> 00:12:31.986
Started saying, "Please let me take out
my pent up feelings; I have no peace of
mind at all."

00:12:31.986 --> 00:12:40.943
I said, "Why?" He said, "This Varna
Nagar that I have built, people
think highly of it,"

00:12:40.943 --> 00:12:45.658
"But I think I have ruined all
the able people."

00:12:46.195 --> 00:12:52.535
There were people here who did not
drink alcohol, so they have started
drinking, business of bad women
has started here,

00:12:52.535 --> 00:12:55.980
Here (UNCLEAR - Republic?) has started,
drugs have started here.

00:12:55.980 --> 00:13:00.012
Such things are happening here
that You won't believe.

00:13:00.012 --> 00:13:11.137
And above all, there are all kinds of
horrible atrocities and extreme
violence here, I don't know why.

00:13:13.810 --> 00:13:18.530
I was very surprised at this. He said,

00:13:18.530 --> 00:13:24.978
"Mother, I did all the work with
good intentions in my heart to
develop this village."

00:13:24.978 --> 00:13:32.351
"With a lot of hard work and desire, I
brought it to such heights of progress.
I built so many schools in it,"

00:13:32.351 --> 00:13:38.597
"built colleges, what all I did
and in the end what is the outcome,"

00:13:38.597 --> 00:13:46.883
"that such corrupt/vicious people that when
I see them in the morning, I feel like
that why should I taint myself?"

00:13:47.493 --> 00:13:53.494
Will drink alcohol the whole night.
Will take small children with them
and they all will drink.

00:13:56.592 --> 00:14:07.782
So whatever good deeds he did,
whatever work he did, that too
went to waste. Still there is
no peace among the people.

00:14:09.054 --> 00:14:18.174
When there was no freedom in our country,
Gandhiji used to say, 'First let freedom
come, then You can start Sahaja Yoga.'

00:14:18.174 --> 00:14:21.305
Until You are not free, how will
You start Sahaja Yoga?

00:14:21.344 --> 00:14:26.604
All right, I said, let freedom come.
That freedom came.

00:14:27.554 --> 00:14:33.594
Many people surrendered their
selves, sacrificed, freedom
came after doing a great deal.

00:14:34.706 --> 00:14:43.916
But now when I look at people,
I wonder where have these cunning
mafia-like people come from after
independence.

00:14:45.090 --> 00:14:50.730
I don't understand. The people of
that time who were fighting,

00:14:50.730 --> 00:14:58.592
who went to prison, those who faced
so many problems, who are these people
who have come instead of them?

00:14:58.878 --> 00:15:07.498
It seems as if these demons have
come and sat in the place of the
gods and goddesses of Heaven.

00:15:07.738 --> 00:15:18.348
How much the society has changed!
Is this why we got independence?
People say a lot of things.

00:15:18.348 --> 00:15:23.714
Recently the people of Bangladesh
told Me that, "We fought so much Mother
that we want Bangladesh,

00:15:23.714 --> 00:15:28.597
want Bangladesh, want Bangladesh.
What did we get from the
independence of Bangladesh?"

00:15:32.138 --> 00:15:38.098
So many people died in Bangladesh and
how much poverty has come in Bangladesh

00:15:39.345 --> 00:15:46.125
that this poverty is never going
to go away.

00:15:46.125 --> 00:15:50.490
This will keep on increasing,
our poverty will keep on
increasing day by day.

00:15:51.204 --> 00:15:54.784
Similar is the condition of the Pakistanis too.

00:15:55.776 --> 00:16:03.346
And if by any means you think that
through this fighting, this trouble
and sacrifice,

00:16:03.346 --> 00:16:11.574
and even if by talking big you achieve
something, you will still feel that
you have not achieved anything.

00:16:13.571 --> 00:16:23.761
Condition will be the same. Like
if you buy a car, then you feel
what car, should buy a house now.

00:16:24.614 --> 00:16:29.164
Bought a house, then will feel,
what is it of the house, my
sister is not married yet.

00:16:29.479 --> 00:16:36.499
In this way only, all the great things
that happened in the world and the
great battles for freedom were fought,

00:16:36.499 --> 00:16:46.323
did this, did that - but today,
no matter which country you go
to, man has become so distracted

00:16:46.323 --> 00:16:54.099
that can't understand that after fighting
so many battles, after becoming so
talented, after making so much progress,

00:16:54.099 --> 00:17:05.584
on what brink is man standing today?
Don't know when he will be destroyed,
when he will be ruined.

00:17:06.131 --> 00:17:13.931
A lot of people who are sitting that
(UNCLEAR), don't know how we're
going to be finished,

00:17:14.388 --> 00:17:23.608
but despite all this, man's quest
is towards peace.

00:17:25.884 --> 00:17:33.964
When there is a search in that too,
many associations are formed. Groups
in the name of this, groups in the
name of that.

00:17:33.964 --> 00:17:39.085
Recently I heard that in the demand
for peace (UNCLEAR).

00:17:39.698 --> 00:17:47.538
I have seen such people also who
have received Nobel Prize for Peace
but are so short-tempered

00:17:49.796 --> 00:17:59.646
and so full of anger that there are
ten thousands of wrinkles on their face.

00:18:01.161 --> 00:18:05.781
And as soon as we see them we feel,
'Oh my God, who is this messenger
of death?'

00:18:07.387 --> 00:18:12.807
and they have got the Nobel Prize
for Peace.

00:18:14.429 --> 00:18:18.049
From which angle did they look at
the person and gave the Nobel Prize?

00:18:18.307 --> 00:18:22.297
And upon asking the people that,
'Oh, are they coming here tomorrow?'

00:18:22.297 --> 00:18:27.966
'Oh my God, just don't ask anything.
Her tongue is like a sword?'

00:18:29.006 --> 00:18:37.176
And such anger that she dances from
here to there, from there to here,
when her temper rises.

00:18:37.737 --> 00:18:47.887
And has got Nobel Prize for Peace.
This world is also a strange drama.

00:18:48.041 --> 00:18:57.841
This alchemy of Kaliyug, all this
was going to happen in this Kaliyug.
This has indeed happened.

00:18:57.880 --> 00:19:06.580
But along with this a very great
blessing has come from God due to
which we (UNCLEAR).

00:19:06.580 --> 00:19:14.884
In which this All-Pervading Power of
God's love has now taken pity

00:19:14.884 --> 00:19:25.188
on man, on his stupidity, that I gave
him freedom to find his freedom
find the Truth,

00:19:25.188 --> 00:19:34.060
search for God, then don't know what
all swirls he is carrying and what
condition he has made of himself.

00:19:35.681 --> 00:19:45.841
Why did it happen like this? Perhaps
it is the Power of Love of the
compassionate God,

00:19:45.841 --> 00:19:55.485
He felt compassion and in that
compassion, His form has changed
in the KritaYuga.

00:19:59.088 --> 00:20:06.338
Today Sahaja Yoga is taking full
advantage of that KritaYuga.

00:20:07.551 --> 00:20:18.451
The advent of KritaYuga and its
manifestation is a great blessing
for us.

00:20:18.692 --> 00:20:28.392
Anyone who does not take advantage
of this (opportunity) at this time,
will indeed be very unfortunate.

00:20:29.710 --> 00:20:44.450
There is no one as unblessed/miserable as the
one who cannot fully achieve the
blessings of this God.

00:20:47.522 --> 00:20:54.832
But in Kaliyug, we have even
lost faith in God.

00:20:54.990 --> 00:21:04.600
We think that God does not exist,
and even if He exists,
He must be sitting somewhere.

00:21:06.196 --> 00:21:14.066
People do not understand anything,
they are looking towards God in
delusion.

00:21:14.719 --> 00:21:23.199
And in order to understand this,
KritaYuga has come for you to
achieve Self-realisation.

00:21:24.379 --> 00:21:40.619
In Self-realisation you reach to
that abode which is the source
of peace. The peace of peace.

00:21:41.983 --> 00:21:52.573
From where peace flows, from where
the stream flows out, and whenever
desired, then also there is peace.

00:21:53.862 --> 00:22:04.322
Such a person is not only calm
himself, but wherever he goes,
there peace resides.

00:22:04.368 --> 00:22:10.778
Suddenly the person starts wondering
that who has come and stood there.

00:22:10.778 --> 00:22:16.844
Early in the morning it seems that
who is this statue of peace who
has come and stood there.

00:22:16.846 --> 00:22:24.366
It was as if peace had started flowing
from within and whatever restlessness
I had felt has vanished.

00:22:27.027 --> 00:22:39.216
Where did all that restlessness that
came from our ego and our mind disappear?

00:22:39.396 --> 00:22:54.536
And in this salty water, in this
salty water of the sea, from where
has a beautiful pond of Peace formed.

00:22:56.088 --> 00:23:06.188
How has this peace surged within
us and has calmed us down.

00:23:06.533 --> 00:23:17.743
And now it seems that all things
are swaying in peace. The speed
of peace has come.

00:23:18.093 --> 00:23:28.763
We think of peace as something
like ice that neither melts nor
spreads.

00:23:29.419 --> 00:23:35.409
Our opinion is this only, a person
whom we call a peaceful person,

00:23:35.409 --> 00:23:39.005
he neither speaks nor moves;
remains seated at his place.

00:23:40.738 --> 00:23:49.178
The peace of a Sahaja Yogi is like ice
but the ice flows

00:23:49.268 --> 00:23:57.647
and whomsoever it touches, it calms
them down, it gives them comfort.

00:23:58.111 --> 00:24:04.491
The alchemy to achieve this peace is
completely created within you by God.

00:24:04.564 --> 00:24:07.674
Has been very beautifully made,
with a lot of love.

00:24:07.826 --> 00:24:16.566
As if an artist is sitting in a
very peaceful place and drawing
a beautiful picture.

00:24:16.717 --> 00:24:22.957
In this way God has created this
beautiful creation within you.

00:24:23.707 --> 00:24:38.097
You don't even know and the peace
that He has filled in that creation,

00:24:38.731 --> 00:24:50.691
it creates peace in all our chakras
at the time of Kundalini awakening.

00:24:52.605 --> 00:24:58.185
This is the power of our Kundalini
passing through the seven chakras.

00:24:59.381 --> 00:25:11.631
And when it passes through each
energy centre, then each energy
centre has a peace of its own,

00:25:15.213 --> 00:25:21.943
its lake that is, it makes it
absolutely calm.

00:25:23.457 --> 00:25:31.637
As if there's a lake in which
there is absolutely no disturbance,
it's a calm lake.

00:25:31.771 --> 00:25:40.371
The beauty spread around that lake
is completely reflected in it
and gives joy.

00:25:40.371 --> 00:25:52.954
Similarly, how in such a person
does the lake of peace get
established in every chakra.

00:25:53.815 --> 00:26:10.025
All the beauty, all the tenderness,
all the love, all the joy that is
spread around it,

00:26:10.450 --> 00:26:16.750
is reflected, but such a person's
life blossoms.

00:26:17.979 --> 00:26:24.029
Many people think that how can Kundalini
be awakened easily like this.

00:26:26.255 --> 00:26:29.955
At least in our country many
people know about Kundalini

00:26:29.955 --> 00:26:35.060
Many do not even know, they are very
ignorant. But they cannot believe this

00:26:35.060 --> 00:26:42.542
that the Kundalini which rises
through great, difficult penance,
how does it rise so easily?

00:26:43.844 --> 00:26:47.464
Our chakras are not yet clean,
our lives are also not clean

00:26:52.430 --> 00:27:02.460
But the KritaYuga has already begun;
Its blessings which you have received

00:27:02.803 --> 00:27:10.034
thus that KritaYuga has brought
this environment/state today,

00:27:10.034 --> 00:27:17.099
that the Kundalini within us is
suddenly, at once awakened.

00:27:18.722 --> 00:27:27.972
And due to this blessing only,
today thousands of people in the
world are realizing their Spirits

00:27:27.998 --> 00:27:33.128
and are attaining that peace which
is the nature of that Spirit.

00:27:33.316 --> 00:27:39.226
Unless peace comes within a person,
he cannot think of anything,

00:27:39.226 --> 00:27:44.329
can't work out anything in a
smooth manner

00:27:44.329 --> 00:27:48.169
and even after doing it, the
satisfaction is not achieved.

00:27:51.726 --> 00:27:57.446
The satisfaction is also not
something so concrete that you
have found the satisfaction.

00:27:57.446 --> 00:28:01.356
Meaning, any such thing you got
in your hands.

00:28:02.464 --> 00:28:13.164
This is also a leaning of the attention,
the form of that instinct is different,
that has changed.

00:28:14.693 --> 00:28:20.013
Just understand, that the instinct/disposition
which was running all around, has been
absorbed/settled within you.

00:28:20.214 --> 00:28:26.514
Those instincts, those tendencies,
all of those tendencies have come
into this life.

00:28:27.229 --> 00:28:34.340
So I said that, 'Now I am sitting in contentment.'
With pure attention I am just seeing.'

00:28:35.959 --> 00:28:48.049
But what is reflecting within you
after finding this contentment?

00:28:48.647 --> 00:28:56.593
Complete peace. So the peace of
this peace is the Kundalini.

00:28:57.049 --> 00:29:03.109
It resides within you and it/She is
your Mother, extremely peaceful.

00:29:04.069 --> 00:29:11.169
She is very calm and knows everything
about you.

00:29:11.425 --> 00:29:17.575
Just as is a tape record, in the same
way this peace has known everything
about you,

00:29:17.875 --> 00:29:23.525
that how is this son of Mine. She
is the Mother within you,
your individual Mother.

00:29:23.818 --> 00:29:28.828
Now She is sitting peacefully.
Many people say that She is
in a dormant state,

00:29:28.828 --> 00:29:37.755
waiting for an opportunity that some
authorized person comes and helps Me
progress in My rising up/upliftment.

00:29:38.667 --> 00:29:49.907
