your head tilted back, ask a question
three times in your mind,

00:56:32.053 --> 00:56:44.053
“Mother, is this the Paramchaitanya?
Mother, is this the same power of peace?”

00:56:44.940 --> 00:56:56.170
“Mother, is this,” one may also
ask that, “Shri Mataji, is this the
All-Pervading Power of God’s love?”

00:56:57.110 --> 00:57:04.380
"Is this the Spiritual power?" Whatever
you want ask the question three times
with your head raised up.

00:57:07.398 --> 00:57:18.768
There is a strong wind blowing.
Put your hands down. Put these
down one by one.

00:57:18.769 --> 00:57:26.919
Oh Baba! This is not Ghaziabad,
this has become Shanti Bagh.

00:57:29.679 --> 00:57:34.329
All of you have got your realization.
Most of the people have got their
realization.

00:57:37.337 --> 00:57:40.127
My greetings to all of you!
